$GDXIN %gdxF%\exp_in.gdx
* Sets to control simulations
$LOADdc sim sim1 simr
$LOADdc demog0

* Sets to control closure rule selection
$LOADdc clos clos1

* Sets to control sensitivity testing
$LOADdc sens sens1

*- Define sets on the basis of read in data
 a1(a) = YES;
 i1(i) = YES;

*----The first sim will always be the baseline calibration sim (i.e. BaU)
 BaUFlag(sim)$(ord(sim) = 1)=1;
 BaUFlag(sim)$(ord(sim) = 2)=2;
*---- unless changed here

*-get BaU out of sim1 if it is not run
 sim1(sim)$(%runBaU%=0 AND BaUFlag(sim)=1) = NO;

